**Field Mapping**:
| Field | Source | Fallback | Type |
|-------|--------|----------|------|
| id | data.id | (none) | string |
| projectId | data.projectId | (none) | string |
| description | data.description | "No description" | string |
| status | data.status | (none) | string (e.g., "completed", "in_progress") |
| createdAt | data.createdAt | (none) | ISO 8601 timestamp |
| expiresAt | data.expiresAt | (none) | ISO 8601 timestamp |
| size | data.size | "Unknown" | string (formatted size) |
