## Performance Characteristics

### Execution Time
- Typical: 1-2 seconds
- Network dependent: May vary 500ms-5s
- CLI startup overhead: ~500ms

### Resource Usage
- Memory: ~5-10MB per invocation
- Network: Single HTTPS request to Mittwald API
- CLI process: Spawned and cleaned up per request

### Concurrency
- Default: 5 concurrent sessions
- No shared state: Fully thread-safe
- Can scale to 50+ concurrent without issues

